metadata.title: Shoreline Seabird/Marine Mammal Count
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds/Mammals; Seabird and marine mammal counts along shorelines of Naked, Storey, Peak and Smith Islands of Prince William Sound. Surveys completed in: June 1978-1980 and 1989-1994. July 1878 and August 1978. Transects were preset Fish and Wildlife transects. The filenames and descriptions are as follows: 1) CENLOG Census log with date, time, conditions, islands 2) CENSPECI # OF EACH SPECIES BY LOG id and shoreline section 3) SECAREA sq/km of each shoreline section 4) SECORD LAT/LONG of each shoreline section
